Calibri; font-size:8pt; text-decoration:underline">http://www.visitengland.org/insight-statistics/major-tourism-surveys/dayvisitors/</span></a><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:8pt"> </span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_ftn16"></a><a href="#_ftnref16">[16]</a><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:8pt"> Marine Conservation Society 2012</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_ftn17"></a><a href="#_ftnref17">[17]</a><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10pt"> Prior, S, (2011) </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10pt; font-style:italic">Investigating the use of voluntary management in the protection of UK marine biodiversity </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10pt">- available at </span><a href="http://www.pembrokeshiremarinecode.org.uk/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/WEL-Voluntary-Marine-Management-2011.pdf"><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:Calibri; font-size:10pt; text-decoration:underline">http://www.pembrokeshiremarinecode.org.uk/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/WEL-Voluntary-Marine-Management-2011.pdf</span></a><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:10pt"> </span></p></body></html>